Package: hw4
Type: Package
Title: Simple Linear Regression
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Yun Zhang
Maintainer: Yun Zhang <yunzh@umich.edu>
Description: This R package performs simple linear regression. 
    This package is for linear regression model with a single explanatory variable and 
    computes basic intercept and slope, performs statistical testing (T-test and F-test),
    calculates R-squared and ajusted R-squared values, and plot linear regression line. 
    This package utlizes S3 generic functions to print user-friendly analysis results. 
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: ggplot2, stats
RoxygenNote: 7.1.2
Depends: 
    R (>= 2.10)
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Config/testthat/edition: 3
